{"id":24769273895,"name":"Test","node_id":"WFR_kwLOA_1uaM8AAAAFxF0gJw","head_branch":"fix_missing_name_oauth2_clients","head_sha":"394f0ea5c48f7a73f005ca081246cf92c1a4d3b8","path":".github/workflows/run-tests.yml","run_number":52829,"run_attempt":1,"event":"pull_request","display_title":"fix: OAuth2 client list endpoint failing when sorting by name","status":"completed","conclusion":"success","workflow_id":10954,"check_suite_id":65670955823,"check_suite_node_id":"CS_kwDOA_1uaM8AAAAPSktDLw","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/24769273895","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/24769273895","created_at":"2026-04-22T08:50:26Z","updated_at":"2026-04-22T09:05:56Z","run_started_at":"2026-04-22T08:50:26Z","jobs_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/24769273895/jobs","logs_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/24769273895/logs","check_suite_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/check-suites/65670955823","artifacts_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/24769273895/artifacts","cancel_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/24769273895/cancel","rerun_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/24769273895/rerun","head_commit":{"message":"fix(sec): drop client_credentials from the admin grant-type allow-list\n\nThe UI only exposes authorization_code + refresh_token checkboxes, so\nletting client_credentials through any admin-input path (REST CRUD or\nbulk /api/metadata) is a bypass that creates a long-lived, non-rotating,\nnon-MFA bearer token acting as the creator. Only the DCR system\nregistrar legitimately needs it — that record is created server-side\nvia Dhis2OAuth2ClientStore.save and bypasses this validator already.\n\nTighten ALLOWED_ADMIN_GRANT_TYPES to {authorization_code, refresh_token}\nand keep one narrow exception in validateGrantTypes: if the clientId is\nthe reserved system-dcr-registrar-client, client_credentials is\naccepted. That lets a full metadata export/import round-trip re-import\nthe registrar unchanged; admins still can't create or rename into it\n(reserved-clientId check fires earlier).\n\nTest: testRejectsClientCredentialsGrantTypeOnAdminCreate replaces the\nearlier testUpdateAllowsClientCredentialsGrantType.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e\nSigned-off-by: Morten Svanaes \u003cmsvanaes@dhis2.org\u003e","author":{"name":"Morten Svanaes","email":"msvanaes@dhis2.org"},"id":"394f0ea5c48f7a73f005ca081246cf92c1a4d3b8","tree_id":"7ecc3db031d336790b492a2a3665efe10e5816ce","timestamp":"2026-04-22T08:50:16Z","committer":{"name":"Morten Svanaes","email":"msvanaes@dhis2.org"}},"workflow_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/workflows/10954","repository":{"id":66940520,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnk2Njk0MDUyMA==","owner":{"login":"dhis2","id":1089987,"node_id":"MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjEwODk5ODc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1089987?v=4","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2","gravatar_id":"","type":"Organization","site_admin":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/events{/privacy}","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/following{/other_user}","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/followers","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/gists{/gist_id}","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/orgs","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/received_events","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/repos","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/subscriptions"},"name":"dhis2-core","full_name":"dhis2/dhis2-core","description":"DHIS 2 Core. Written in Java. Contains the service layer and Web API.","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2